(1, 'About', '1761221697.jpeg', '<p dir=\"ltr\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">At Neurigo 360, we are dedicated to providing exceptional physical therapy and rehabilitation services to patients with neurological disorders and mobility challenges in Noida, Uttar Pradesh. Our mission is to empower individuals to regain their independence, enhance their functionality, and improve their quality of life through personalized, evidence-based care. As the leading physiotherapy center in the region, we strive to set the standard for excellence in neurological rehabilitation, offering innovative solutions and a patient-centric approach that makes a meaningful difference.</p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6b8eec69-7fff-8396-3935-06b06934fbfc\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">We are aware of the significant effects that injuries, neurological disorders, or limited mobility can have on a person\'s life</span>. Our goal is to support our patients holistically, addressing their physical, emotional, and psychological needs to help them achieve their fullest potential. Whether it’s recovering from a stroke, managing Parkinson’s disease, or rehabilitating after a spinal cord injury, Neurigo 360 is committed to being a trusted partner in every patient’s recovery journey.</p></span><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Who We Are</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Neurigo 360 was founded with a vision to redefine physical therapy and rehabilitation in Noida. Our state-of-the-art facility combines cutting-edge technology, advanced therapeutic techniques, and a team of highly skilled professionals to deliver unparalleled care. We pride ourselves on creating a welcoming, supportive environment where patients feel motivated and empowered to take charge of their recovery.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">Our team consists of certified physical therapists, rehabilitation specialists, and support staff who are passionate about making a difference. Each member is trained in the latest rehabilitation techniques and stays updated on advancements in physical therapy to ensure the highest standard of care. We work collaboratively with patients, their families, and other healthcare providers to create comprehensive, individualized treatment plans that address unique needs and goals.</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Our Philosophy: Personalized, Compassionate Care</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">At Neurigo 360, we believe that every patient is unique, with distinct challenges, aspirations, and circumstances. Our philosophy is rooted in delivering personalized care tailored to each individual’s specific needs. We take the time to understand our patients’ conditions, lifestyles, and objectives to design treatment plans that are both effective and sustainable.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">Compassion is at the core of our approach. We recognize that many of our patients are navigating difficult circumstances, and we strive to create a kind, encouraging environment that fosters hope and resilience. Our therapists are not only skilled clinicians but also empathetic partners who provide support and motivation throughout the recovery process. By combining evidence-based practices with a patient-centered mindset, we ensure that every individual receives the care and respect they deserve.</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Our Founder: Dr. Kunwar Pratap Singh</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Neurigo 360 was established by Dr. Kunwar Pratap Singh, a visionary leader driven by a passion for serving those with neurological impairments. In a world that often overlooks individuals with disabilities,&nbsp;<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81ee92a2-7fff-6b6e-6f49-aee05d2f8b56\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">to give these patients the support and care they require to flourish, Dr. Singh launched Neurigo 360</span></span>. His commitment to societal impact over personal gain sets him apart as a compassionate innovator in the field of rehabilitation.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">With a background of working in various organizations,&nbsp;<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bbd6e98d-7fff-e983-6f11-d9dcea362411\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Dr. Singh founded Neurigo 360, a company committed to providing top-notch care, with his knowledge and commitment</span></span>. His vision is to make Neurigo 360 a global leader in neurological rehabilitation by leveraging cutting-edge technology, refining treatment processes, and prioritizing patient outcomes. Through perseverance, innovation, and hard work, Dr. Singh aims to significantly reduce recovery times for underserved patients worldwide, enabling them to walk again and reintegrate into society with confidence.</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Why Choose Neurigo 360?</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Neurigo 360 stands out as the premier choice for physical therapy and rehabilitation in Noida for several reasons:</p><ul class=\"tight\" data-tight=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Expertise and Experience</strong>: Our team of certified physical therapists and rehabilitation specialists has extensive experience working with neurological disorders. We stay abreast of the latest research and techniques to provide evidence-based, effective care.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Personalized Treatment Plans</strong>: We design individualized therapy plans that incorporate a range of evidence-based modalities, ensuring that each patient’s unique needs and goals are addressed.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>State-of-the-Art Facilities</strong>: Our modern clinic is equipped with advanced technology and equipment, including robotic-assisted gait trainers, functional electrical stimulation devices, and a hydrotherapy pool, to support optimal recovery.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Compassionate Environment</strong>: We foster a warm, supportive atmosphere where patients feel valued, respected, and motivated to achieve their goals.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Collaborative Approach</strong>: We prioritize open communication and collaboration with patients, their families, and healthcare providers to ensure a cohesive and effective treatment experience.</p></li></ul><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Our Commitment to the Community</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Beyond our clinic, Neurigo 360 is deeply committed to the Noida community. We actively engage in health awareness campaigns, free screening camps, and educational workshops to promote injury prevention, posture correction, and chronic condition management. By empowering individuals with knowledge and resources, we aim to enhance overall community health and well-being.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">We also partner with local hospitals, clinics, and healthcare providers to ensure a seamless continuum of care for our patients. These collaborations strengthen our ability to deliver comprehensive services and make a lasting impact on the lives we touch.</p><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Our Approach to Care</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">At Neurigo 360, we believe that successful rehabilitation requires a combination of clinical expertise, advanced technology, and genuine care. Our approach emphasizes:</p><ul class=\"tight\" data-tight=\"true\" dir=\"ltr\"><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Individualized Therapy</strong>: Every patient receives a customized treatment plan based on thorough evaluations, including functional movement analysis, to address the root causes of their condition.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Evidence-Based Practices</strong>: We utilize proven techniques such as neurodevelopmental treatment, constraint-induced movement therapy, and functional electrical stimulation to enhance mobility, strength, and coordination.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Holistic Support</strong>: We address the physical, emotional, and psychological aspects of recovery, providing encouragement and guidance to help patients overcome challenges.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Intensity and Repetition</strong>: Our therapies are designed to maximize recovery through targeted, intensive interventions that push patients toward their functional goals.</p></li><li><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Patient Empowerment</strong>: We involve patients in their treatment plans, fostering a sense of ownership and motivation to achieve lasting results.</p></li></ul><h2 dir=\"ltr\">Your Journey Starts Here</h2><p dir=\"ltr\">Neurigo 360 is more than a physiotherapy center—it’s a place where hope, healing, and transformation come together. We are dedicated to helping you overcome neurological challenges, regain your mobility, and live life to the fullest. Whether you’re seeking recovery from a specific condition or aiming to improve your overall function, our team is here to guide you every step of the way.</p><p dir=\"ltr\">We invite you to visit our clinic in Noida and experience the Neurigo 360 difference. Contact us today to schedule a consultation and take the first step toward a healthier, more independent future. Together, we can achieve extraordinary outcomes.</p>', 1, '2025-05-07 04:51:57', '2025-11-05 08:01:34');

